1935;;Honours Easy;;British;;Herbert Brenon;;Greta Nissen, Patric Knowles, Margaret Lockwood;;drama;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Honours_Easy;;Unhinged art dealer William Barton (Ivan Samson) seeks revenge on a man who ruined his career years ago. He does so by attempting to frame the man's son for the theft of $2,500 from the safe in his gallery. However the son has an alibi in Barton's wife, with whom he is having an affair.